dc_description_s: 1 map on 9 sheets : color ; on sheets 65 x 55 cm Statement of responsibility: Sanborn Map Company. Partial cadastral map. Title from sheet 1. Sheets 8 and 9 at a scale of 1:1,200. Copyright 1925 by the Sanborn Map Company.' '(1983) (9 sheets)'--in upper right corner of sheet 1. '(1983)'--in upper right corner of sheets 2-9. Oriented with north to the upper right on some sheets. 'January 1925.' Adjoining sheets index map on sheet 1 also shows radial distances from the Borough Building. Includes location map, sheet index map at a scale of 600 feet to 1 inch, key, streets and 'Specials' indexes, notes, and text.'  Scale approximately 1:600 ; Scale [1:1,200]. 100 ft. to an in.
